<i>noun</i>: 곡류천 [공뉴천], 곡류 [공뉴] <i>verb</i>: 굽이치다 [구비치다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>곡류천 [공뉴천]</dt><br>
<dd>winding stream; meander</dd><br>
<dd>이리저리 구부러져 흘러가는 하천.</dd><br>
<dd>A stream running in curves.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>곡류 [공뉴]</dt><br>
<dd>winding stream; meander</dd><br>
<dd>물이 구부러져 흘러감. 또는 그 흐름.</dd><br>
<dd>Water streaming in curves or the stream.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>굽이치다 [구비치다]</dt><br>
<dd>wind; meander</dd><br>
<dd>물이 굽이를 이루며 흐르다.</dd><br>
<dd>For water to flow in twists and turns.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>